ont-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif">A very popular crypto thing these da=
ys is what I=E2=80=99ll loosely call =E2=80=9Clending programs.=E2=80=9D Yo=
u own some cryptocurrency coins, you pop them into some sort of pool, the p=
ool uses your coins to make money (by market making, or by proprietary trad=
ing, or by lending them out to people who want to borrow crypto), and the p=
ool shares the money it makes with you. Lots of =E2=80=9Cyield farming=E2=
